<headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 01 at 4:24PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Scattered showers and thunderstorms to affect Southwest MT this
evening...
At 425 PM, scattered showers and thunderstorms are developing over
Southwest MT. These storms will generally move to the east around
20 mph and will move through Southwest MT through 7 PM.
The main impact from any storms will be lightning and brief heavy
rainfall. Some storms could also produce wind gusts up to 30 mph.</description>
